snippet.title: Try this new sandbox simulator soon !
snippet.description:
Dive into a world of creation and discovery, where each element combines to form new ones. Experiment freely in this interactive sandbox. But be careful: every combination has its consequences..

LINK & PLS add to wishlist : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3262420/Alchemy_Laboratory_Simulator/
